  "text": "Measure of the anticoagulant activity Anticoagulant activity was measured by the APTT-based one-stage clotting time assay. Normal pooled plasma was used as the substrate, and the clotting time was recorded after adding appropriate amounts of each retentate [CITATION_1] .",
